\end{array}\right|=\begin{array}{cccccc}
+ & a_{1}b_{2}c_{3} & + & a_{2}b_{3}c_{1} & + & a_{3}b_{1}c_{2}\\
- & a_{1}b_{3}c_{2} & - & a_{2}b_{1}c_{3} & - & a_{3}b_{2}c_{1}
\end{array}$
